          </aside>
        </div>

        <article className="dashboard-panel dashboard-panel-wide">
          <div className="dashboard-panel-header with-badge">
            <div>
              <h3>Tabla Ejecutiva por ├ürea</h3>
              <p>Resumen general consolidado aunque existan m├║ltiples tableros y fuentes operativas.</p>
            </div>
            <span className="dashboard-alert-pill">{dashboardAreaRows.length} ├íreas</span>
          </div>
          <div className="dashboard-table-wrap">
